		<div class="social-comment-meta social-comment-meta-wordpress">
			<span class="social-posted-from">
								<span>View</span>
							</span>
			<a href="http://longorshortcapital.com/le-natures-disaster.htm/comment-page-1#comment-128158" class="social-posted-when" target="_blank">December 24, 2008</a>
